PN,38601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782805680
OL,3,CWater quality monitors installed to
OL,4,Chelp preserve rare chalk streams
OL,6,FNineteen monitors to measure the
OL,7,Fquality of the water have been
OL,8,Finstalled in rare chalk streams in the
OL,9,Fsouth.
OL,11,FThey've been put at different
OL,12,Flocations between the mouth and the
OL,13,Fsource along the rivers Test, Itchen
OL,14,Fand Blackwater.
OL,16,FSouthern Water says the real-time data
OL,17,Fcollected will help build up a picture
OL,18,Fof the health of the water.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
