OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782805680
OL,3,CWater quality monitors installed to
OL,4,Chelp preserve rare chalk streams
OL,6,FJoff Edevane, Environment and Water
OL,7,FQuality lead, said: "Rather than a
OL,8,Fnormal sampling programme where we'll
OL,9,Ftake a spot sample, take it back to
OL,10,Fthe lab and it's just a quick snapshot
OL,11,Fof what happened when you were there
OL,12,Ffor 30 seconds, this continuously
OL,13,Fmonitors water quality for 24 hours,
OL,14,Fseven days a week.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782805680
OL,3,CWater quality monitors installed to
OL,4,Chelp preserve rare chalk streams
OL,6,F"It looks at some key parameters,
OL,7,Fwhich is basically indicative of good
OL,8,For poor water quality, so things like
OL,9,Fdissolved oxygen, ammonia, pH and
OL,10,Ftemperature, so we are installing
OL,11,Fthese completely up and down the Test
OL,12,Fand its tributaries."
OL,14,FChalk streams are rivers that rise
OL,15,Ffrom springs in areas with chalk
OL,16,Fbedrock. They tend to have clear,
OL,17,Fclean, water making them ideal
OL,18,Fhabitats for fish - like salmon and
OL,19,Ftrout - and other wildlife.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782805680
OL,3,CWater quality monitors installed to
OL,4,Chelp preserve rare chalk streams
OL,6,FEcologically they are very important
OL,7,Fand some of the world's most
OL,8,Fcelebrated chalk streams are located
OL,9,Fin Hampshire and Dorset.
OL,11,FBut in recent years many of these
OL,12,Ffragile sites have been threatened by
OL,13,Ffactors like sewage dumping,
OL,14,Fagricultural and road run-off and
OL,15,Fclimate change.
OL,17,FSouthern Water is working on the
OL,18,Fproject with the Pan Parishes River
OL,19,FPollution Forum and local riverkeepers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782805680
OL,3,CWater quality monitors installed to
OL,4,Chelp preserve rare chalk streams
OL,6,FCouncillor Geoff Cooper, from Test
OL,7,FValley Borough Council, is also a
OL,8,Frepresentative of the forum.
OL,10,FHe said: "The monitors are a massive
OL,11,Fstep forward from where we were a
OL,12,Fcouple of years ago.
OL,14,F"If we were able to deliver this in
OL,15,Fall of our major chalk streams and all
OL,16,Fof our rivers and waterways, then the
OL,17,Famount of data that would become
OL,18,Favailable, and the amount of instant
OL,19,Fimpact we can have on the quality of
OL,20,Fthe rivers, will really start to make
OL,21,Fa difference.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782805680
OL,3,CWater quality monitors installed to
OL,4,Chelp preserve rare chalk streams
OL,6,F"This is about monitoring the rivers.
OL,7,FThe action still needs to be taken to
OL,8,Fprotect them."
OL,10,FBy 2030, all water companies must
OL,11,Finstall monitors and publish the data
OL,12,Fupstream and downstream of their
OL,13,Foutfalls.
OL,15,FThe riverkeepers, who look after and
OL,16,Fmaintain the rivers, decided where the
OL,17,Fremaining monitors should be placed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782805680
OL,3,CWater quality monitors installed to
OL,4,Chelp preserve rare chalk streams
OL,6,FRiverkeeper Seth Crosswaite said:
OL,7,F"We're hoping to build a picture over
OL,8,Ftime. It's not going to be instant. We
OL,9,Fwill be able to see what the river is
OL,10,Factually doing, looking after itself,
OL,11,Fwhether we need to intervene in places.
OL,13,F"We can see the full length of the
OL,14,Friver, so if there is a pollution
OL,15,Fincident, we can look upstream and
OL,16,Fdownstream of it and see how that
OL,17,Fpollution incident is affecting the
OL,18,Friver directly. "
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782805680
OL,3,CWater quality monitors installed to
OL,4,Chelp preserve rare chalk streams
OL,6,FSouthern Water say the project is part
OL,7,Fof the utility company's #160m
OL,8,Finvestment in improving water quality
OL,9,Fand enhancing the local environment in
OL,10,FHampshire.
OL,12,FThe data from the monitors will be
OL,13,Favailable to the public in the next 12
OL,14,Fmonths.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
